<div class="hero-section">
    <h1>Welcome to Agri-Energy Connect 🌿</h1>
    <p>
        Empowering South African farmers with sustainable agriculture and clean energy.
        From soil to solar — build a better tomorrow 🌞💧🌽.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section green">
    <h2>🌱 Platform Overview</h2>
    <p>
        Agri-Energy Connect is a digital hub that blends agriculture with renewable energy. Whether you're tracking production, learning new techniques, or exploring solar power for your farm, this platform gives you the tools to thrive.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section yellow">
    <h2>⚡ Core Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Sustainable Farming Hub:</strong> Learn organic growing, water efficiency, and soil health.</li>
        <li><strong>Green Energy Marketplace:</strong> Browse solar, wind, and bio-based technologies.</li>
        <li><strong>Learning & Development:</strong> Access expert-led webinars and guides.</li>
        <li><strong>Collaborative Projects:</strong> Join forces with others to apply for funding or share knowledge.</li>
        <li><strong>Role-Specific Tools:</strong> Dashboards built for both 👩‍🌾 Farmers and 👨‍💼 Employees.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="section blue">
    <h2>👩‍🌾 For Farmers</h2>
    <p>
        Farmers can manage profiles, track harvests, upload product images, and explore innovations that support higher yield and climate resilience. Get community insights, discover financing, and grow smarter.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>👨‍💼 For Employees</h2>
    <p>
        Employees help keep the platform healthy by managing farmer onboarding, verifying data, and ensuring smooth operations. With insights and tools built just for them, they support a more efficient, connected farming future.
    </p>

    <a class="learn-link" href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core" target="_blank">
        📘 Learn more about ASP.NET Core
    </a>
</div>
